'''魯霍拉·扎姆'''（{{lang-fa|روح‌الله زم}}，{{bd|1978年|7月27日|2020年|12月12日|catIdx=Zam}}），[[伊朗|伊朗]]記者、異見人士。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-50045089|title=Ruhollah Zam: Iran 'arrests exiled journalist' for fanning unrest|website=BBC|date=2019-10-14|language=en|accessdate=2020-12-12|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112024324/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-50045089|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.rferl.org/a/iran-exile-telegram-channel-roohollah-zam-bring-down-government/28957053.html|title=Controversial Exile Using Social Media To Try To Bring Down Iranian Government|last=Najibullah|first=Farangis|date=2018-01-05|work=Radio Free Europe|accessdate=2018-01-08|language=en|archive-date=2020-09-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200922064028/https://www.rferl.org/a/iran-exile-telegram-channel-roohollah-zam-bring-down-government/28957053.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>2015年，他創建名為「Amadnews」的[[Telegram|Telegram]]頻道。在[[2017－2018年伊朗示威|2017－2018年伊朗示威]]中，扎姆積極報導，發放示威活動的時間和官員的負面信息。<ref name="AP">{{Cite news|url=https://apnews.com/78a46cea167e4f94ada0a690b7f2f3db|title=Protests in Iran fanned by exiled journalist, messaging app|work=AP News|access-date=2017-12-31|language=en-US|last=Gambrell|first=Jon|archive-date=2017-12-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171231170953/https://apnews.com/78a46cea167e4f94ada0a690b7f2f3db|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{tsl|en|Voice of America Persian News Network|美國之音波斯語頻道}}經常邀請扎姆出席其節目。<ref name="A"/><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.thedailybeast.com/the-app-powering-the-uprising-in-iran|title=The App Powering the Uprising in Iran, Where Some Channels Pushed for Violence|work=The Daily Beast|access-date=2018-01-11|language=en-US|archive-date=2019-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190201192853/https://www.thedailybeast.com/the-app-powering-the-uprising-in-iran|dead-url=no}}</ref>2020年6月，伊朗法庭指他經營一個很受歡迎的反政府論壇是「塵世腐敗」，當局認為論壇煽動了[[2017－2018年伊朗示威|2017－2018年伊朗示威]]。他被法庭判處死刑並在同年12月12日執行。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-53238000?intlink_from_url=https://www.bbc.com/news/topics/cjnwl8q4ggwt/iran&link_location=live-reporting-story|title=Ruhollah Zam: Iran sentences journalist to death for fanning unrest|work=BBC|language=en-GB|accessdate=2020-12-12|archive-date=2020-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200724155913/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-53238000?intlink_from_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Ftopics%2Fcjnwl8q4ggwt%2Firan&link_location=live-reporting-story|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.dw.com/zh/%E5%9C%A8%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97-%E4%B8%80%E5%90%8D%E8%AE%B0%E8%80%85%E8%A2%AB%E7%BB%9E%E5%88%91%E5%A4%84%E6%AD%BB/a-55916060 |title=在伊朗 一名记者被绞刑处死 |language=zh-hant |date=2020-12-12 |accessdate=2020-12-12 |work=德國之聲 |archive-date=2020-12-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201212181945/https://www.dw.com/zh/%E5%9C%A8%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97-%E4%B8%80%E5%90%8D%E8%AE%B0%E8%80%85%E8%A2%AB%E7%BB%9E%E5%88%91%E5%A4%84%E6%AD%BB/a-55916060 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 生平 ==
1978年，扎姆生於德黑蘭一個家庭。<ref name="A">{{Cite news|url=https://thearabweekly.com/tehrans-campaign-against-opposition-raises-questions|title=Tehran’s campaign against the opposition raises questions|work=The Arab Weekly|access-date=2019-03-17|language=en-US|last=Alfoneh|first=Ali|archive-date=2020-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200703125917/https://thearabweekly.com/tehrans-campaign-against-opposition-raises-questions|dead-url=no}}</ref>他的父親穆罕默德·阿里·扎姆是[[伊朗改革派|伊朗改革派]]人士，是1980至1990年代的高級政府官員。<ref name="AP"/>在[[伊朗綠色革命|伊朗綠色革命]]後，魯霍拉·扎姆反對執政者，被判在[[埃温监狱|埃温监狱]]監禁。後來，扎姆離開伊朗逃亡到法國。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.bild.de/politik/ausland/bild-international/telegram-interview-iran-protest-54371208.bild.html|title=With highspeed internet, the regime would be gone in a month|work=Bild|access-date=2018-01-04|language=en-US|last=Abri|first=Ehsan|archive-date=2019-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190809173746/https://www.bild.de/politik/ausland/bild-international/telegram-interview-iran-protest-54371208.bild.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2019年10月14日，伊朗革命衛隊宣稱他們已經把扎姆引渡回伊朗並拘捕他。他的保安亦在其擁有100萬追踪者的Telegram頻道發佈他被捕的消息。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.bbc.com/persian|title=ایستگاه خبر؛ دوشنبه ۲۲ مهر ماه ۱۳۹۸|website=BBC Persian|language=fa|access-date=2019-10-14|archive-date=2019-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191117163430/https://www.bbc.com/persian|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2020年初，聆訊在德黑蘭的革命法院第15分院展開，由法官{{link-en|Abolqasem Salavati}}主持<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.tasnimnews.com/en/news/2020/02/10/2200329/first-trial-session-of-ruhollah-zam-held-in-tehran|title=First Trial Session of Ruhollah Zam Held in Tehran - Politics news|website=Tasnim News Agency|language=en|access-date=2020-02-11|archive-date=2020-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200701002656/https://www.tasnimnews.com/en/news/2020/02/10/2200329/first-trial-session-of-ruhollah-zam-held-in-tehran|dead-url=no}}</ref>，魯霍拉·扎姆最終被判處死刑。<ref>{{cite web |last=Karimi |first=Nasser |title=Iran journalist who fueled 2017 protests sentenced to death |url=https://www.ctvnews.ca/world/iran-journalist-who-fueled-2017-protests-sentenced-to-death-1.5005313 |website=CTV News |date=2020-06-30 |language=en |accessdate=2020-12-12 |archive-date=2020-12-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201212181945/https://www.ctvnews.ca/world/iran-journalist-who-fuelled-2017-protests-sentenced-to-death-1.5005313 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2020年12月12日，他被[[絞刑|絞刑]]處決，享年42歲。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20201212/s00005/1607778012213/%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E7%95%B0%E8%A6%8B%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E9%81%AD%E7%B5%9E%E5%88%91%E8%99%95%E6%B1%BA |title=伊朗異見記者遭絞刑處決 (20:52) |publisher=明報 |language=zh-hk |date=2020-12-12 |access-date=2020-12-12 |archive-date=2020-12-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201212181953/https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20201212/s00005/1607778012213/%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E7%95%B0%E8%A6%8B%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E9%81%AD%E7%B5%9E%E5%88%91%E8%99%95%E6%B1%BA |dead-url=no }}</ref>

